{"title":"HackTheBox 第0层","uid":"a467409ab1e50dee76a1d026b53d85d3","slug":"HackTheBox 第0层","date":"2023-11-23T05:08:23.603Z","updated":"2023-11-23T05:08:23.604Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/HackTheBox 第0层.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/6.jpg","content":"<p>平台地址：<a href=\"https://www.hackthebox.com/\">https://www.hackthebox.com/</a></p>\n<p>我这里选择的是自己下载vpn，用kali来作为攻击机<img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/OTP2TRuU715UsWEJ.png!thumbnail\" title=\"fig:\"></p>\n<p>下载UDP 1337，TCP实测会比较慢并且不太稳定</p>\n<p>导入到openvpn中</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/2Ki5QZfn93uz0geS.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>kali中使用命令openvpn进行连接</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo openvpn openvpn文件</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>挂好vpn确保脸上之后下发靶机<br><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/9O2oBK8A50lgw0BC.png!thumbnail\" title=\"fig:\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"Meow\"><a href=\"#Meow\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Meow\"></a><strong>Meow</strong></h1><p>先ping一下看看</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/VrdvKL5Rl4X8v6A1.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>通了之后证明该IP能够成功被访问到</p>\n<p>接着用nmap进行扫描</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/Ur3Di8AVYx83jBaz.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>发现23端口开放并且服务是telnet</p>\n<p>获取了一些基本端口信息之后看看问题</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/sSjazpFWa4mkNSd3.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>上网查找一下，指的就是虚拟机</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：Virtual Machine</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/C5YFMdd1exnBy5pK.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>指的是终端</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：terminal</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/v7fHItdN5NzS194s.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：openvpn</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/E6Mg8PNw9olm5gZk.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：TUN</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/XiiuOFrO7T78i6XA.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>利用回显测试连接，我们知道Ping方法使用的是ICMP协议</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：Ping</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/lnhWt6x19pUAIJwe.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>找端口的工具就是刚才使用的nmap</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：nmap</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/ATbNRAVU2MHfLhLp.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>刚才扫描出来了</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：telnet</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/G3JYPe4xLwOFnYkU.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>题目询问什么用户不需要密码登录，查找资料</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>Telnet协议是TCP&#x2F;IP协议族中的一员，是Internet远程登录服务的标准协议和主要方式。<br>可以使用telnet命令进行登录远程主机</p></blockquote>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">telnet IP</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/exlmlnDvlWYBcjfz.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>并且root用户是可以进行免密登录的</p>\n<p>接下来查看路径并且使用命令获取flag</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ls</span><br><span class=\"line\">cat flag.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/Ual3U6wWJYBMx5ss.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"Fawn\"><a href=\"#Fawn\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Fawn\"></a><strong>Fawn</strong></h1><p>同样的，拿到靶机先扫描一下端口</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/a9zd2Q5UEeNBrfYh.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>发现21端口是开着的，显示ftp服务，看看问题</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/tysE9ByDDIcE9gmh.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>搜索FTP全称</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：FileTransferProtocol</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/b1CTDivCBAOzIDuc.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>根据刚才扫描的结果可以知道端口为21</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：21</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/Ned74zdGfECoP406.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>搜索得到SFTP</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：SFTP</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/xC7ZdfvCnHIlBgua.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：PING</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/kyLoZxlhZIMrqUv4.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>根据之前的nmap扫描可以知道版本是vsftpd 3.0.3</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：vsftpd 3.0.3</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/4MKlktVoxIJWzPZm.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：UNIX</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/priNyydkcHyR7cTx.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/FzHpND5NTLHYyjJV.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：ftp -h</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/SBuy1QPapU6F2THk.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>没有帐户的情况下登录使用anonymous</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：anonymous</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/aJ8j0BA7jK5XluJt.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>登陆成功的响应码，登录之后查看</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/7PElE3jWwEItj7fW.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：230</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/6EKNK3ijEUKFMSDx.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>列出可用的文件和目录的命令</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：ls</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/03cvF043yvcezVzQ.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>下载ftp服务器上找到文件的命令为get</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：get</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>根据之前问题的提示，拿flag</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ls</span><br><span class=\"line\">get flag.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/jTUPKo3bSfeREsgq.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>可以看到flag.txt文件被从ftp服务器上下载到了本地</p>\n<p>接着在本地进行cat就可以了</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/KMlhEoHiyKZU9Pzl.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"Dancing\"><a href=\"#Dancing\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Dancing\"></a><strong>Dancing</strong></h1><p>扫描IP</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/lXcI0aKMiCO7VdbL.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/liifb5b4zLEyo66l.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>搜SMB全程就行</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：Server Message Block</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/FUvrjdQUSBhfonzB.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>上网搜索SMB的端口</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/9vM7T9md3ga89OWM.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：445</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/vVtkQxEglB99P4qw.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>根据扫描结果查看445端口的服务为microsoft-ds</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：microsoft-ds</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/FRYQCt0LKTeFBL43.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>问的是SMB命令（smbclient）查看共享资源的参数，参数为-L</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：-L</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/qHBIKPvaTcAECtvf.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>使用smbclient命令连接查看服务端分享的资源</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">smbclient -L IP</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>连不上的多连几遍，可能是vpn的问题，访问不太稳定<br><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/1AsVdLRCVc4gNFaT.png!thumbnail\" title=\"fig:\"></p>\n<p>没有密码直接回车就好，问题问的是有几个共享文件</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：4</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/WNB1lpFIjJuPmq7f.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>这里能无密码连接的共享文件就是最后一个WorkShares</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：WorkShares</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/njjXbUlU72JrQrOA.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>同样问下载文件的命令</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：get</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>接下来就是拿flag了，首先先连接共享文件</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">smbclient \\\\\\\\IP\\\\WorkShares</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>这里也是多连接访问几次，或者把vpn关掉重开</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ls</span><br><span class=\"line\">cd James.P</span><br><span class=\"line\">ls</span><br><span class=\"line\">get flag.txt/more flag.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/OUEJ1M9OO33i1n4M.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>这里根据之前题目的提示可以知道最终get下载flag.txt文件（下载好之后直接本地cat就好）</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/jU4JgizLyQ2kb5w4.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>但同时也可以使用more命令直接查看flag，如下图所示</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/KAP9JpmmAGaBU44n.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"Redeemer\"><a href=\"#Redeemer\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Redeemer\"></a><strong>Redeemer</strong></h1><p>扫描下IP，看看开放的端口</p>\n<p>可能是vpn的问题，我一直都没有扫出来对应开放的端口，所以看了下网上的wp</p>\n<p>发现开放的是6379端口，考的应该是redis未授权漏洞</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/M2slLxovhkRz2jI2.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>这个问的就是开放的端口</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：6379</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/G6jzmg7ri6I8aBfV.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>询问开放端口上的服务</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：Redis</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/daSHcOLmCJEqSa9R.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>选择题选择第一个</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：In-memory Database</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/vSbvxjB3JkAQ1klw.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>询问能连接redis服务器的命令</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：redis-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/FHTnoAmO6lvChzsz.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>命令所使用标记主机的参数</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：-h</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/pEftZSW3Lt5nMlgd.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>查看服务器信息的命令</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：info</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/SQ7DrBiakkIbJ6oG.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>redis版本，连接上之后使用info命令查看版本</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo redis-cli -h IP</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/jfnAB2h0WjWcZnbQ.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：5.0.7</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/oE66G9aNWeyf2ype.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：select</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/4QquahbNqlv8hub8.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>索引为0的数据库有多少个键，在之前的info信息中寻找信息</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/HAkUznIOPKuzl56v.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：4</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/T5NEqrqGJQNrPvo0.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>查看所有键的命令</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">答案：keys *</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>接下来获取最后的flag</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">get flag</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/ZMrijMJoDucgKRgV.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n","text":"平台地址：https://www.hackthebox.com/ 我这里选择的是自己下载vpn，用kali来作为攻击机 下载UDP 1337，TCP实测会比较慢...","permalink":"/post/HackTheBox 第0层","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"渗透","slug":"渗透","count":3,"path":"api/categories/渗透.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"渗透","slug":"渗透","count":3,"path":"api/tags/渗透.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Meow\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Meow</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Fawn\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Fawn</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Dancing\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Dancing</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Redeemer\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Redeemer</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"nnnpc","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/img/2.jpg","link":"/","description":"安全萌新","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{"title":"HackTheBox 第1层","uid":"33536bd0778d1c4be97b54513f70c062","slug":"HackTheBox 第1层","date":"2023-11-23T05:26:24.046Z","updated":"2023-11-23T05:26:24.048Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/HackTheBox 第1层.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/6.jpg","text":"Appointment 1答案：Structured Query Language 1答案：SQL injection 最常见的sql漏洞就是sql注入了 1答...","permalink":"/post/HackTheBox 第1层","phot